| [[File:Apple A6 Chip.jpg|100px]]
| [[32 nanometer|32&nbsp;nm]] [[HKMG]]<ref name="Chipworks-A6" /><ref name="A6Teardown">{{cite web |url=http://www.ifixit.com/Teardown/Apple-A6-Teardown/10528/ |title=Apple A6 Teardown |publisher=IFixit |date=September 25, 2012}}</ref>
